---
title: Carb Smart Beef Moussaka with Roasted Eggplant and DIY Béchamel
description: This cozy comfort food is light on carbs! Roasted eggplant adds silky texture and hearty Mediterranean flavour to this dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/moussaka-de-boeuf-24ce5bd0.jpg
